steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"

When I add new table with Name "jitdash00601" and Comment "Testing"
When I add new table with Name "jitdash00602" and Comment "Testing"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash00601" displayed in dashboard list
Then I should see table Name "jitdash00602" displayed in dashboard list
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
When I delete the table with Name "jitdash00602"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see table Name "jitdash00601" displayed in dashboard list
Then I should NOT see table Name "jitdash00602" displayed in dashboard list
